家人的关系。","name":"麦家琪","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"麥家琪，香港女藝人、演員、主持人，別名麥方喬，香港成長，前無綫電視及亞洲電視女藝員及節目主持人，入行前是模特兒。","name":"麥家琪","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"FR","iso_639_1":"fr","name":"Français","english_name":"French","data":{"biography":"Teresa Mak Ka-Kei (en chinois : 麥家琪) est une actrice hongkongaise sous contrat avec ATV. Elle a participé au concours Miss Hong Kong en 1993.","name":"","primary":false}}]}},"person_4898723_translations":{"at":1773384112786,"data":{"id":4898723,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"NO","iso_639_1":"no","name":"Norsk","english_name":"Norwegian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Ronny Oksvold","primary":true}}]}},"tv_297424_detail_vi-VN":{"at":1773426814428,"data":{"adult":false,"backdrop_path":"/1H3IzlKJGjX78Gt4MWFmWeqHral.jpg","created_by":[{"id":5950560,"credit_id":"696f20e55264cca6a6fe107f","name":"Jung Yeo Jin","original_name":"Jung Yeo Jin","gender":0,"profile_path":null},{"id":5950562,"credit_id":"696f2130b106b7c81ee0a952","name":"Lee Hyeon Seok","original_name":"Lee Hyeon Seok","gender":0,"profile_path":null}],"episode_run_time":[60],"first_air_date":"2026-02-04","genres":[{"id":35,"name":"Phim Hài"},{"id":18,"name":"Phim Chính Kịch"}],"homepage":"https://tvn.cjenm.com/ko/Our-Universe","id":297424,"in_production":false,"languages":["ko"],"last_air_date":"2026-03-11","last_episode_to_air":{"id":6804533,"name":"Episode 12","overview":"","vote_average":0,"vote_count":0,"air_date":"2026-03-12","episode_number":12,"episode_type":"finale","production_code":"","runtime":61,"season_number":1,"show_id":297424,"still_path":"/7goVIyICcrv78uGHKse896T4Z5T.jpg"},"name":"Vũ Trụ Của Đôi Ta","next_episode_to_air":null,"networks":[{"id":866,"logo_path":"/aRDq8zBrX3YLpHSfueNQBkNnn7b.png","name":"tvN","origin_country":"KR"}],"number_of_episodes":12,"number_of_seasons":1,"origin_country":["KR"],"original_language":"ko","original_name":"우주를 줄게","overview":"","popularity":27.5